38
00:02:15,730 --> 00:02:17,013
and it cut it clean open.

39
00:02:18,900 --> 00:02:21,180
I was so angry though.

40
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:26,053
I stood up right there
with blood everywhere.

41
00:02:28,385 --> 00:02:29,835
