148
00:07:59,010 --> 00:08:02,730
Lord, if it is your will
that I go home to you soon,

149
00:08:02,730 --> 00:08:06,267
let it be so, but please don't take her.

150
00:08:11,438 --> 00:08:13,267
- [Doctor] Hi Becky, it's
